    TSelectionModalDecorator
    public abstract class TDynaViewSelectionBaseDecorator<M extends TModelView>
extends TDynaViewSimpleBaseDecorator<M>
    The basic decorator of the open modal view to select an entity. It can be set using the TSelectionModalPresenter annotation on the TEntityModelView.
    Author:
    Davis Gordon

      Modifier and Type Method Description
      void buildAddButton​(java.lang.String text)
      Build a button for the add action.

      If the parameter was null this will use the text set up in @TPresenter{decorator= @TDecorator{addButtonText=''}} but if the given TModelView was not annotated with TPresenter or with a custom view annotation which contains a TPresenter a default string (TAnnotationDefaultValue.TVIEW_addButtonText) will be used.

      This will initialize with "t-button" id.
